OL,3,C'Loving' granddad died after falling
OL,4,Cthrough hole left by builders in floor
OL,6,FA building company has been fined
OL,7,F#150,000 and ordered to pay #50,000
OL,8,Fcosts after a grandfather fell to his
OL,9,Fdeath through a hole left by workers
OL,10,Fin his bathroom floor.
OL,12,F81-year-old Kenneth Armitage from York
OL,13,Ffell through the inadequately secured
OL,14,Fhole and landed on the kitchen floor
OL,15,Fbelow in an incident which his
OL,16,Fdaughter Suzy said "should never have
OL,17,Fhappened."
