OL,3,C'Loving' granddad died after falling
OL,4,Cthrough hole left by builders in floor
OL,6,FThe bathroom in Mr Armitage's house in
OL,7,FHuntingdon, York was being converted
OL,8,Finto a wet room by the construction
OL,9,Fcompany Cooper and Westgate.
OL,11,FThe company had removed the room's
OL,12,Ffloorboards as it accessed pipework,
OL,13,Fbut left an unguarded hole in the
OL,14,Ffloor on 8 February 2019.
OL,16,FMr Armitage later fell through the
OL,17,Fhole and was found dead by his son-in-
OL,18,Flaw the following evening.
