OL,3,C'Loving' granddad died after falling
OL,4,Cthrough hole left by builders in floor
OL,6,FA Health and Safety Executive (HSE)
OL,7,Finvestigation found Cooper and
OL,8,FWestgate failed to adequately secure
OL,9,Fthe hole as its employees were not
OL,10,Fproperly trained. The company had also
OL,11,Ffailed to undertake a suitable and
OL,12,Fsufficient risk assessment, or a
OL,13,Fmethod statement for the work involved.
OL,15,FKenneth's daughter, Suzy, said: "Our
OL,16,Fdad, who was sadly taken away from us,
OL,17,Fwas everything to us. He was the
OL,18,Fkindest person you could ever meet.
