OL,3,C'Loving' granddad died after falling
OL,4,Cthrough hole left by builders in floor
OL,6,F"He was a fantastic dad to me, my
OL,7,Fbrother and a loving grandad to all
OL,8,Four children.
OL,10,F"I can't believe he has gone, I keep
OL,11,Fthinking it's a horrible nightmare and
OL,12,FI will wake up and he'll be there. Our
OL,13,Fhearts were broken that day and may
OL,14,Fnever heal. It should have never
OL,15,Fhappened.
OL,17,F"We are all still struggling to come
OL,18,Fto terms with losing him."
