OL,3,C'Loving' granddad died after falling
OL,4,Cthrough hole left by builders in floor
OL,6,FHSE inspector Yolande Burns-
OL,7,FSleightholme said: "Employers need to
OL,8,Ffully assess and control the risks
OL,9,Ffrom holes in domestic properties and
OL,10,Frecognise the importance of securing
OL,11,Fthem effectively. They should then
OL,12,Fpass this knowledge on to their
OL,13,Femployees through suitable training
OL,14,Fand guidance.
OL,16,F"This incident could so easily have
OL,17,Fbeen avoided had Cooper and Westgate
OL,18,Fproperly assessed the risks, put in
OL,19,Fplace safe working practices and
OL,20,Fprovided the correct training to its
OL,21,Femployees."
